### GraphQL - Liste des réservations
POST http://localhost:8080/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "query { reservations { id dateDebut dateFin client { nom prenom } } }"
}

### GraphQL - Consulter une réservation
POST http://localhost:8080/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "query { reservation(id: 1) { id dateDebut dateFin preferences client { nom prenom email } chambre { type prix } } }"
}

### GraphQL - Créer une réservation
POST http://localhost:8080/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "mutation { createReservation(input: { client: { nom: \"Dupont\" prenom: \"Jean\" email: \"jean.dupont@example.com\" telephone: \"0123456789\" } chambre: { id: 1 } dateDebut: \"2024-06-01\" dateFin: \"2024-06-05\" preferences: \"Vue sur mer\" }) { id dateDebut dateFin } }"
}

### GraphQL - Modifier une réservation
POST http://localhost:8080/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "mutation { updateReservation(id: 1, input: { dateDebut: \"2024-06-02\" dateFin: \"2024-06-06\" }) { id dateDebut dateFin } }"
}

### GraphQL - Supprimer une réservation
POST http://localhost:8080/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "mutation { deleteReservation(id: 1) }"
}

